Summary: I saw it fly right over my house.
divs: Sighting DetailsBefore i saw the object i was about to fall asleep. I noticed it when the house started vibrating. When i saw it at first i thought it was a plane but it did not make any noise. It looked like i triangle with several lights surrounding the extirior. When i saw it i was shocked and didn't know what to do. I lost sight of it when it flew over to the other side of my house.
